{
  "stem": "1918.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we arrived and were confronted with Mengele, and the smoke, and the stench of burning flesh, and the Sonderkommando, and the people who came to empty the cattle cars and threw everybody down.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my sister and I were looking for our luggage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wanted to get it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the guy said, what are you looking for?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we said, for our cigarettes, and she-- and he said-- a young guy, he said-- in the striped clothes-- and he said, you don't need your cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tomorrow you'll be sorry you were ever born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we couldn't imagine what he could mean by that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can there be anything on the face of the earth worse than the cattle car ride?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we found out that that was a cocktail party in comparison to what came after that, when we lived with the stench of burning flesh.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As many as 10,000 to 24,000 people a day were burned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How did you know that was burning flesh that you were smelling?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were were the figures-- how we knew that it was burning?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Even today my kids shield me from a dark smoke if we cross the bridge to go to Jersey or wherever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the smoke was so thick, oozing out of the five chimneys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the stench-- do you know what a-- what the stench of a-- when you singe a chicken, as Jews do sometimes?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The singeing, the melting down, the burning. 10,000 to 20,000-- 24,000 human beings a day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The stench, 50 years later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You do not know what is lodged in my nostrils.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unbelievable I can recall the stench of burning flesh from this distance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I not only can recall it, I cannot not recall it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
